<div id="middle">
  <div class="banner">
    <div class="banneroneforth">
      <h1>In App Notifications to Mobile Users</h1>
      <p>
        Show notifications to relevant users instantly to increase conversions e.g. you 
        can show a particular notification to users who come from a certain website or, who
        have come to  our site multiple times. In depth Analytics available.
      </p>

      <% if current_user.blank? %>
        <a class="button-img" href="/signup">Create Campaign</a>
      <% else %>
        <a class="button-img" href="/member/campaigns/twitter">Create Campaign</a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="banneronethird">
      <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fbappshq-assets/datas/71089/large.png" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="features-hig"><h2>Features Highlights</h2>
      <div class="app-feature">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <h5>Easy Integration</h5>
            <p>
              Include our Android SDK once and then show custom notifications
              in your app without ever having to bother engineering team.
              This SDK allows you to run all types of mobile campaigns available through us.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h5>Audience Groups</h5>
            <p>
              Create custom audience groups and then run targeted marketing
              campaigns for them e.g. Users who have bought a product on your mobile
              app can be a group and all users who have launched your app more than
              10 times can be another group.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h5>Launch Instantly</h5>
            <p>
              Launch campaigns with in seconds of including SDK in your app. It
              takes a simple click to turn notifications on/off. Also, you can run multiple
              notifications at the same time - one for each audience group.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h5>Custom Styling</h5>
            <p>You can change look and feel as well as content of notifications almost
              instantly by simply going to dashboard and click on few links.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>
